0.006   2020-05-31  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium; Backward-Compatible: no

	- [incompatible] Rename filter 'Str::lowcase' to 'Str::lowercase'.

        - Reinstate filter 'Str::downcase' [RT#132743].

        - [ux] add aliases 'Str::uc' & 'Str::uppercase' for 'Str::upcase',
          'Str::lc' for 'Str::downcase'.

        - Add filters 'Str::ucfirst' & 'Str::lcfirst'.


0.005   2020-05-30  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium; Backward-Compatible: no

	- [incompatible] Rename rule 'Str::downcase' to the more familiar
          'Str::lowcase'. UPDATE: 'Str::downcase' restored in 0.006.


0.004   2020-02-11  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Add filter: Str::replace_map.


0.003   2020-02-11  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Add might_fail support (like in Data::Sah::Coerce) in the filter
	  rules. We want it after all to use filter rules as checkers. Add
	  return_type 'val' as well as 'str_errmsg+val'.

	- Add filter: Str::check (perl only for now, mostly to demo might_fail).


